<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "oppanGwanakStyle.css" %>
    <title>관악구 맛집 백과 - 배달/포장</title>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-light">
        <div class="container-lg outsidenav">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">관악구 맛집 백과</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapsibleNavbar">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapsible navbar-collapse" id="collapsibleNavbar">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/lightfoods">가벼운 식당</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/heavyfoods">무거운 식당</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item active">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/takeoutfoods">배달/포장</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <div class="container-lg">
            <div class="page-header text-center p-4 mb-3 text-dark-50 rounded">
                <h1 class="titlehead display-4 mb-2">배달/포장</h1>
                <p class="lead mb-0">사진을 누르시면 더 자세한 정보를 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
            </div>

            <% @takeoutfoods.each do |takeoutfood| %>
            <div class="card mb-3">
                <div class="card-body text-center text-sm-left border border-warning shadow">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-8 col-sm-7">
                            <h1><%= takeoutfood.title %></h1>
                            <p class="lead"><%= takeoutfood.address %></p>
                            <p class="description"><%= takeoutfood.text %></p>
                            <p>
                            <span class="btn btn-warning p-0"><%= link_to '수정하기', edit_takeoutfood_path(takeoutfood), :class => "btn" %></span>
                            <span class="btn btn-warning p-0"><%= link_to '삭제하기', takeoutfood_path(takeoutfood), method: :delete, data: { confirm: '정말 삭제하시겠습니까?' }, :class => "btn" %></span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-5 align-items-center d-flex">
                            <a href="<%= takeoutfood.webpage %>" target="_blank"><img
                                    src="<%= takeoutfood.imagelink %>" alt="<%= takeoutfood.title %>"
                                    class="img-fluid border rounded border-muted"></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% end %>
            
            <div class="text-center">
            <a class="btn btn-warning mb-3" href="/takeoutfoods/new" role="button">새 식당 추가</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>


    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container-md">
            <p class="text-muted mt-2 mb-1">본 페이지는 송상록(2019-12213, 심리학과)의 웹프로그래밍개론 수업 실습용 페이지입니다.</p>
            <p class="text-muted mb-1">식당 사진은 송상록 본인이 촬영했습니다.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
</body>

</html>